            <div>
                <strong>Hard Skills:</strong><br>
                <span class="skill-tag">MS Excel</span> <span class="skill-tag">Market Research</span>
                <span class="skill-tag">Business Analysis</span> <span class="skill-tag">PowerPoint</span>
            </div>
            <div>
                <strong>Languages:</strong><br>
                <span class="skill-tag">English (Working)</span> <span class="skill-tag">Chinese (HSK3)</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>🎯 Career Objective</h2>
        <p>I aim to pursue a career in import-export or international business, where I can apply my academic knowledge and continuously develop my professional skills.</p>
    </section>
</div>

</body>
</html>
